 Once upon a time there was a man named Manfred Simmons, who lived in a small town of 
Biverly in England. He was very happy man and had a wife named Jane Rose and they had a
son named Theobold Simmons.

    His son was in second grade and his studies were going well. But one day he and his
wife got call from the school that their son didn't come to school tht day.

    They were astonished to hear that as they went to the school in the morning to drop
off their son to the school.

This is plot 2
